paying only Rs 20 to Rs 30 per kilogram.\n\nIt is said the cost of production of the farmers is Rs 37.5 per kilogram.\n\nKaji said the price the entrepreneurs were offering them, Rs 20 per kilogram, is peanuts and the farmers would be at loss at this price.\n\nThe farmers have demanded that the tea entrepreneurs return their green tea if they are not willing to give the appropriate price for their produce.\n\nRSS","title":"Ilam tea farmers in protest mood - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/01/124236/","video":[]}
